byline.original: By P.J. PHILIP Wireless to THE NEW YORK TIMES

snippet: PARIS, Dec. 31--The new year is beginning with a sure confidence that if it does not bring victory it will at least see the beginning of victory and the establishment of a new order in Europe. It is not going to be easy....

headline.main: FRENCH START '40 WITH CONFIDENCE; Beginning of Victory Leading to Establishment of a New Order in Europe Seen MEN ON LEAVE CHEERFUL Racing Resumed at Vincennes --People No Longer Face the Future With Terror

lead_paragraph: PARIS, Dec. 31--The new year is beginning with a sure confidence that if it does not bring victory it will at least see the beginning of victory and the establishment of a new order in Europe. It is not going to be easy.
